    <item>
      <title>Wilson 球拍制造商 Amer 着眼于中国市场以阻止 IPO 后股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/amer-eyes-china-sales-resilience-to-halt-post-ipo-stock-slide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自今年早些时候上市以来，Amer Sports Inc. 一直令投资者感到失望，自 2 月上市以来，其股价已下跌约 9%。但这种情况可能会在周二发生改变，华尔街希望通过其最新收益来提振股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/amer-eyes-china-sales-resilience-to-halt-post-ipo-stock-slide</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 12:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
